## 7. Fancy Indexing
### 7.1 Using Boolean mask

a = np.random.randint(0,20,15)
print(a)
mask = (a % 2 == 0)
even_numbers = a[mask]
print(even_numbers)
a[mask]=-1 #it can be very useful to assign a new value to sub array
print(a)


### 7.2. Using Integer Array

a = np.arange(0,100,10)
print(a)
b = a[[2,3,5,2,4]]
print(b)
a[[9,7]] = -200
print(a)
print(b)
